fields.name: Classic White Cotton Shirt
fields.description: A timeless classic — this white cotton shirt is perfect for both casual and formal wear. Made from breathable, high-quality cotton, it offers comfort and durability with a clean and stylish look.

fields.name: Denim Jacket - Blue Wash
fields.description: A versatile blue wash denim jacket with a vintage look. Made from 100% cotton with metal buttons and two front flap pockets. Ideal for layering in all seasons.

fields.name: Slim Fit Black Jeans
fields.description: Comfortable and stretchy black jeans designed with a modern slim fit. Perfect for everyday wear with durability and style.

fields.name: Nike Air Max 270
fields.description: The Nike Air Max 270 delivers visible cushioning under every step. Inspired by iconic Air Max models, it features a bold heel unit and sleek design perfect for all-day comfort and streetwear style. Breathable mesh upper and dual-density foam ensure a smooth, responsive ride.

fields.name: Harry Potter and the Sorcerer’s Stone
fields.description: The first book in the globally bestselling Harry Potter series by J.K. Rowling. Follow Harry as he discovers he’s a wizard, attends Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry, and faces the dark wizard who killed his parents. A magical tale of friendship, courage, and adventure.
